```
@observable = tracked state
@action     = mutates observables
observer    = subscribes the UI
```
In this app the observer is mobx-angular's *mobxAutorun directive: action mutates → MobX notifies → *mobxAutorun re-renders that region.

Memoize the in-flight promise:
```
if (this.p) return this.p;
this.p = this.doMigrations();
```
Concurrent callers await the SAME run → migration executes once → no double-import.
